One-Punch Folk Song

00:11:03.503 --> 00:11:06.256
"I have an old enemy I must defeat!

00:11:06.548 --> 00:11:09.092
Please take me as your disciple,
Master Saitama!”

00:11:18.935 --> 00:11:20.604
(Ah, that's the way,
that's the way)

